title: "Water in the fossil-free transition"
excerpt: "Changing climate is leading to increased stresses, variability, and uncertainty for water resources from reservoirs to river basins. However, continuing advances in monitoring, data sharing, supercomputing, modeling, and machine learning may offer a path for better informed complex watershed-scale decisions, particularly in underserved communities."
